{"tid":225709,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李本瀅曾撐佔中罵政府","createTime":"2017-05-02T03:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T04:37:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43356176aad93a25f85cfdfec14b7b5e1ae8251c","tid":225709,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:42:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20008426&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20008426%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170502&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=6c35bdd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20008426%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170502&h=c34c083f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20008426&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170502</a><br />\n<br />\n李本瀅曾撐佔中罵政府<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n李本瀅<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】撰文反擊梁特謬誤的天文台前台長李本瀅，1979年加入天文台，2000年升為航空氣象服務科助理台長，2009年接替林超英成為台長，至2011年退休，任期不足兩年。他在任期間屢被質疑延遲發出颱風訊號，加上坊間流傳「李氏力場」的講法，令人懷疑有商業考慮只掛「假日波」。李最終發表千文字網誌，引用科學數據回應外界批評。<br />\n李卸任後，不時就時事在其個人網誌發表意見，其中2014年底曾就佔中撰文力撐學生，形容9.26罷課是為了公義；稱9.28響出87枚催淚彈反映政府未能與時並進；更指政府離地、議會不為民發聲、中港文化落差、防暴手法錯配、新聞資訊扭曲，「這是一個荒旦的社會。政府不能以理服眾，因為背後欠了公義」。<br />\n另一前台長林超英，雖然曾為梁振英參選特首撰寫環保政綱被視作「梁粉」，但近年他亦多次表態反對梁治下特區政府政策，包括反對興建機場第三條跑道，又竭力守護郊野公園，與政府欲開發郊野公園建屋立場打對台。<br />\n■記者馬志剛<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n環團斥梁歪理轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n現任台長隱藏帖文補鑊<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n炮轟「港累內地有霧霾」無常識前天文台長K.O.689「南風」論<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;5小時前"},{"pid":"ea00178e55c50b6d0e372ae8c71cd9abd2f246f0","tid":225709,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:43:29.000Z","msg":"李本瀅<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170502/large/12042854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170502%2Flarge%2F12042854.jpg&h=2e2f9d84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f039dc727172e4bafa413f98c1fcbce1bf9e2dce","tid":225709,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a916b5032e4be47bef2556597fd4396c3b0ff20","tid":225709,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:44:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb282ebe62a0d02f3765e3894049bef4717f881d","tid":225709,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地以事論事<br />\n蘋果起尻人講過d咩做乜柒</blockquote><br />\n蘋果冇乜分析力<br />\n唔用資料充撐頁面點夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c13471980fb721aea0f99a837e552c953cfc813","tid":225709,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T04:37:08.000Z","msg":"有良心既學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}